{"tid":1098029,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[書蟲] 有無90後00後睇晒衛斯理系列","createTime":"2019-04-08T18:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T05:41:47.000Z","uid":128109,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"fa4b5dca7ca0537b1b91002331ef958ccd8123f8","tid":1098029,"uid":128109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T18:53:53.000Z","msg":"剛剛睇完鏗鏘集講倪匡論共產黨。諗返起真係要多謝老豆介紹我睇衛斯理小說，我仲記得第一本係地底奇人。最正就係鬼混，藍絲逼溫寶裕推倒。仲有原振俠班女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇書習慣就係個時開始培養，一發不可收拾。到而家仲係書不離手，仲好反共添。有無巴絲一樣，屌晒成套衛斯理。黎緊畢業決定屌埋原振俠系列。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDhAZ6O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDhAZ6O.jpg&h=60520563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/56kCtZ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F56kCtZ8.jpg&h=85cbbdd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bG38AE9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbG38AE9.jpg&h=76124482&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8822fda3ec51fb175b110671cb6f3c4a2865dfe6","tid":1098029,"uid":153496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T18:55:28.000Z","msg":"樓主幾歲開始有睇書嘅習慣"},{"pid":"b858344197663da87145b004ec27aa7c71fb26ed","tid":1098029,"uid":67346,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T19:02:12.000Z","msg":"我記得最初就係大廈<br />\n之後就鑽石花 支離人 紅月亮 藍血人慢慢追<br />\n當時中學圖書館都有50-60本，1日2本咁一個學期追哂館藏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就上網睇txt檔搵未睇嘅書慢慢睇哂"},{"pid":"2196849809fed43eb177015b1cf41d5d47fd7bc1","tid":1098029,"uid":67346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T19:06:54.000Z","msg":"不過補充返佢後期換咗出版社後嘅系列好撚悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全程做安樂椅偵探同